    },
    {
      "id": "eq_6796",
      "raw": "Omega^a_b = (1/2) R^a_{bcd} e^c ^ e^d",
      "type": "comment",
      "context": "e(TM) = (1/(2pi)^n) * Pf(Omega) where Omega is the curvature 2-form matrix (with values in so(2n)).",
